data.description: Meticulously Maintained & Move-In Ready Home Being SOLD FULLY FURNISHED!! Great Opportunity to Purchase One of the Largest Lots in The Links Estates!! This Home is Truly a Gardener's Dream with Your Very Own Citrus Trees, Grape & Blackberry Vines & Flowering Rosebushes. This Spotless 2 Bed, 2 Bath Plus Bonus Room sits on a Wonderful 7027 SF Pie-Shaped Lot.  This Gated 55+ Active Adult Community is True Pride of Ownership where you OWN YOUR LAND!! This Oversized Manufactured Home sits on slab foundation and has a 2-car carport, driveway with Parking for 6 and a Private 14x16 Workshop!   You'll fall in Love with the Colorful Curb Appeal and Cozy Covered patio where you can welcome your friends & family. This Incredible Open Concept Floorplan features Kitchen with Rich Wood Cabinetry, Large Center Island w/Breakfast Bar & Separate Breakfast Nook.  This Home has Big Open Living Spaces including Living Room with Vaulted Ceiling and Bonus Flex Space perfect for Office or 2nd Retreat. The Oversized Master Bedroom has Large Closet & Adjoins the Ensuite Bath with Walk In Shower w/Glass Enclosure, On Split Wing is a Large Guest Bedroom and Hall Bath with Full Tub/Shower and separate Linen. The Interior Laundry Room has Upper Cabinets & Extra Storage. In the Backyard you will enjoy a Fun Outdoor Living Space for Morning Coffee or Evening BBQ!  AWESOME LOCATION with Wonderful Link Estates Clubhouse, Community Activities, Pool Complex and Much More. This Home is LIKE NEW!! Convenient Location off 24 Fwy near Ironwood & Ocotillo.  At the Footstep to Future Shopping, Theatre & Live/Work Multiplex...You will have Community Trail for Convenient Needs & Entertainment. 5 Minutes to Ellsworth Marketplace and Lot of Shopping & Dining!!
